WEBVTT

00:00:00.873 --> 00:00:03.296
It was just an ordinary Saturday.

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.536
My dad was outside mowing the lawn,

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:07.816
my mom was upstairs folding laundry,

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:09.976
my sister was in her room doing homework

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.360
and I was in the basement
playing video games.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.416
And as I came upstairs
to get something to drink,

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:16.656
I looked out the window

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.976
and realized that there was something
that I was supposed to be doing,

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:21.200
and this is what I saw.

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:26.976
No, this wasn't
my family's dinner on fire.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:29.640
This was my science project.